data.description: Experience the perfect blend of convenience and tranquility with this stunning ranch-style home. Situated in a prime location, this property offers the ultimate in comfortable living. As you step inside, you'll be immediately captivated by the open floor plan and the welcoming ambiance of vaulted ceilings. The spacious living, dining, and kitchen areas seamlessly connect, providing an ideal space for relaxation and entertainment. This home features not one, but two main primary bedrooms, one on the main floor and one in the basement, each complete with its own ensuite bathroom. This is an exceptional feature that adds convenience and versatility, making it perfect for multi-generational living or accommodating guests in style. Step outside to your private backyard oasis, where a well-maintained above-ground pool beckons on warm days. The backyard offers a serene space for outdoor enjoyment and relaxation. The large 3 car garage has more than enough room for all your vehicles and all your storage needs!
